            "Hello"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "哈嘍，我叫 Lin，很高興認識你。"
          }
        },
        {
          "en": "She waved and said hello to her neighbors.",
          "highlight": [
            "hello"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "她揮手向鄰居們打招呼。"
          }
